<doc id="772587" wikidata="Q5454268" url="?curid=772587" title="Firstar Center">
<text>Firstar Center was the name previously used by two buildings before Firstar Corporation changed its name to U.S. Bancorp. The two buildings are now named:

*U.S. Bank Center, a high-rise in Milwaukee, Wisconsin
*U.S. Bank Arena, an indoor arena in Cincinnati, Ohio</text><links>
